1
00:01:43,842 --> 00:01:45,396
So romantic

2
00:01:46,650 --> 00:01:49,693
Yuan Lang didn't send you flowers or ring
when he proposed to you?

3
00:01:49,893 --> 00:01:54,021
He sent me

4
00:01:54,221 --> 00:01:56,873
Panna cotta and Foniuduo

5
00:01:57,073 --> 00:01:57,573
Zhu Xuan

6
00:01:57,735 --> 00:01:58,421
Yes?

7
00:01:58,621 --> 00:02:00,164
You are really a foodie

8
00:02:00,364 --> 00:02:01,592
Go away

9
00:02:02,975 --> 00:02:04,079
What are you talking about

10
00:02:04,279 --> 00:02:05,922
Xiao Zi,here you are

11
00:02:06,122 --> 00:02:10,611
We are talking about when you can get married

12
00:02:10,811 --> 00:02:13,207
I'm only 18 years old
I'm not in a hurry

13
00:02:14,930 --> 00:02:16,688
Doctor Lin

14
00:02:16,888 --> 00:02:21,429
You are a famous golden bachelor in the city

15
00:02:21,629 --> 00:02:24,759
How about marrying Ye Zi

16
00:02:24,959 --> 00:02:26,673
What are you saying

17
00:02:26,873 --> 00:02:27,723
Zhu Xuan

18
00:02:27,923 --> 00:02:33,093
If I'm really be with her,
I won't give you the wedding present

19
00:02:33,293 --> 00:02:35,715
Dare you?

20
00:02:35,915 --> 00:02:39,443
Excuse me,I have to go there and check
You can walk around by yourself

21
00:02:39,643 --> 00:02:40,625
Go

22
00:02:40,825 --> 00:02:41,501
Bye

23
00:02:45,632 --> 00:02:47,153
Too many words

24
00:02:47,353 --> 00:02:48,625
My fault

25
00:02:48,825 --> 00:02:50,109
I'm thinking for you

26
00:02:50,309 --> 00:02:53,136
Now it's my fault

27
00:03:09,809 --> 00:03:12,403
Did she refuse you

28
00:03:19,453 --> 00:03:22,483
Haven't you proposed?

29
00:03:27,941 --> 00:03:29,143
Coward

30
00:03:35,914 --> 00:03:40,917
Everything was helping you that day

31
00:03:41,117 --> 00:03:48,063
You will regret if you continue hesitating

32
00:04:24,517 --> 00:04:25,413
Ye Zi

33
00:04:28,318 --> 00:04:29,082
Ye Zi

34
00:04:29,300 --> 00:04:30,540
What happened

35
00:04:40,080 --> 00:04:50,080
02. Restraint

36
00:05:17,640 --> 00:05:20,680
Old man

37
00:05:23,112 --> 00:05:24,060
Old man

38
00:05:26,905 --> 00:05:27,945
What to learn today

39
00:05:28,145 --> 00:05:31,366
I'm busy
Draw by yourself

40
00:05:33,270 --> 00:05:34,583
Funny

41
00:06:36,447 --> 00:06:38,140
Give me your Ipod

42
00:06:39,560 --> 00:06:43,920
Ipod?

43
00:06:44,040 --> 00:06:46,260
Not with me

44
00:06:57,846 --> 00:06:58,935
What

45
00:07:02,120 --> 00:07:03,386
Are you in love?

46
00:07:07,945 --> 00:07:10,579
How come
Who can conquer me

47
00:07:10,779 --> 00:07:14,549
True
You are handsome after all

48
00:07:14,749 --> 00:07:19,066
Funny？

49
00:07:21,700 --> 00:07:24,574
Do you know what I've observed from your painting

50
00:07:26,940 --> 00:07:27,802
What

51
00:07:31,191 --> 00:07:32,278
Restraint

52
00:07:38,604 --> 00:07:42,301
There're only two reasons
if someone starts to control himself

53
00:07:42,501 --> 00:07:43,966
One

54
00:07:46,541 --> 00:07:48,493
He has met some difficulties

55
00:07:48,693 --> 00:07:49,872
Two

56
00:07:50,072 --> 00:07:52,760
He wants to hide his own heart

57
00:07:52,960 --> 00:07:57,536
And you are hiding that you are in love

58
00:08:00,591 --> 00:08:01,528
Nonsense

59
00:08:03,118 --> 00:08:06,176
Painting is the same as life

60
00:08:06,376 --> 00:08:10,385
You must learn to face your true heart

61
00:08:10,585 --> 00:08:12,211
True heart

62
00:08:17,963 --> 00:08:18,979
Old man

63
00:08:19,179 --> 00:08:20,414
You ruined my painting

64
00:08:26,591 --> 00:08:29,774
Forget about your painting

65
00:08:33,657 --> 00:08:35,444
I've spent the whole morning on it

66
00:08:35,644 --> 00:08:36,822
I've spent 10 minutes

67
00:08:43,093 --> 00:08:45,173
Let's do it together

68
00:08:47,024 --> 00:08:47,954
What are you doing

69
00:08:53,889 --> 00:08:54,831
Not bad

70
00:08:55,031 --> 00:08:57,062
Add some here

71
00:08:57,262 --> 00:08:59,405
Right

72
00:08:59,605 --> 00:09:01,969
Right

73
00:09:16,107 --> 00:09:17,351
Get me one more

74
00:09:20,578 --> 00:09:23,358
A big news spreaded in school

75
00:09:23,558 --> 00:09:24,470
Do you know

76
00:09:24,670 --> 00:09:28,441
I may know

77
00:09:28,641 --> 00:09:30,150
Be serious

78
00:09:30,350 --> 00:09:34,224
The school hunk is chasing after the talent girl in Department of Tradition Chinese Painting

79
00:09:34,424 --> 00:09:35,583
You've heard it too

80
00:09:35,783 --> 00:09:37,160
Far more than that

81
00:09:37,360 --> 00:09:40,090
I've experienced it in person

82
00:09:40,290 --> 00:09:42,015
What?He's chasing after you?

83
00:09:44,323 --> 00:09:45,243
I'm not that charming

84
00:09:45,443 --> 00:09:54,207
He's chasing Ye Zi

85
00:09:54,407 --> 00:09:55,012
Really?

86
00:09:55,212 --> 00:09:56,680
Of course
I'm not lying

87
00:10:00,738 --> 00:10:03,566
But things didn't went well between them

88
00:10:03,766 --> 00:10:07,782
We,as sisters,should help them

89
00:10:07,982 --> 00:10:09,308
How

90
00:10:14,486 --> 00:10:17,035
Hi,do you need help

91
00:10:17,235 --> 00:10:19,259
It's you

92
00:10:20,858 --> 00:10:21,904
Why are you hiding

93
00:10:22,104 --> 00:10:24,953
Show some respect

94
00:10:26,408 --> 00:10:28,024
Did you see my iPod

95
00:10:33,547 --> 00:10:35,390
-Is it broken?
-No

96
00:10:38,352 --> 00:10:41,838
I didn't bring it with me today
Give it back next time

97
00:10:44,220 --> 00:10:46,119
Tell me which class you are in

98
00:10:46,319 --> 00:10:50,320
Tell me yours
I'll send it to you

99
00:10:52,876 --> 00:10:53,859
OK

100
00:11:04,911 --> 00:11:06,234
Don't forget

101
00:11:21,645 --> 00:11:22,794
I know who you are

102
00:11:22,994 --> 00:11:25,793
But it's broken

103
00:11:49,430 --> 00:11:50,153
Don't touch it

104
00:11:50,353 --> 00:11:54,299
My son got it through difficulties
It's precious

105
00:11:54,499 --> 00:11:56,168
Only one in the whole world

106
00:11:56,368 --> 00:11:57,702
Don't be mad at me

107
00:11:57,902 --> 00:11:59,223
It's just a signed poster

108
00:12:03,103 --> 00:12:07,742
I heard that it's hard to get their posters

109
00:12:07,942 --> 00:12:11,165
Maybe the boss is kidding

110
00:12:11,365 --> 00:12:13,208
I've seen the genuine ones

111
00:12:13,408 --> 00:12:17,324
This looks really genuine

112
00:12:20,661 --> 00:12:24,761
I remembered
I heard that her son is a director

113
00:12:24,961 --> 00:12:26,216
I didn't believe it before

114
00:12:26,416 --> 00:12:29,254
Now I believe it's true

115
00:12:32,103 --> 00:12:35,444
If it's mine,
that would be so great

116
00:12:35,644 --> 00:12:36,663
Really?

117
00:12:45,998 --> 00:12:49,636
-You are the fan of Little Tigers?
-Right

118
00:12:51,718 --> 00:12:53,488
Are you serious?

119
00:12:53,688 --> 00:12:55,436
You are just like my mom

120
00:12:55,636 --> 00:12:57,348
I just like them

121
00:13:03,287 --> 00:13:04,500
Master

122
00:13:05,742 --> 00:13:11,298
This poster

123
00:13:11,498 --> 00:13:12,480
I want to buy

124
00:13:12,680 --> 00:13:14,822
All posters are not for sale

125
00:13:19,374 --> 00:13:20,462
What are you doing

126
00:13:23,406 --> 00:13:24,500
How about this

127
00:13:24,700 --> 00:13:27,788
Not for sale

128
00:13:27,988 --> 00:13:31,284
Don't mess around

129
00:13:31,484 --> 00:13:34,211
You don't sell for even 300 yuan?

130
00:13:34,411 --> 00:13:36,618
Are you blackmailing

131
00:13:36,818 --> 00:13:40,254
Just go

132
00:13:42,742 --> 00:13:43,525
What are you doing

133
00:13:43,725 --> 00:13:45,558
It should be my question

134
00:13:45,758 --> 00:13:48,182
Have you lost your mind
that you wanted to spend 300 yuan on a poster

135
00:13:48,382 --> 00:13:49,156
Hold it

136
00:13:51,550 --> 00:13:54,247
I want to send it to you because you like it

137
00:13:54,447 --> 00:13:56,200
To me?

138
00:13:56,400 --> 00:13:56,900
Right

139
00:13:57,048 --> 00:13:57,924
How's that

140
00:13:58,124 --> 00:14:02,918
You are so lucky to have me

141
00:14:04,668 --> 00:14:07,124
What do you want

142
00:14:07,324 --> 00:14:09,021
Nothing

143
00:14:09,221 --> 00:14:11,100
It's just because you like it

144
00:14:14,642 --> 00:14:15,850
tell me the reason

145
00:14:16,050 --> 00:14:17,458
Nothing

146
00:14:17,658 --> 00:14:19,628
I'll leave

147
00:14:20,849 --> 00:14:22,563
I say

148
00:14:22,763 --> 00:14:27,449
I wanted to take this poster as a thanking gift

149
00:14:27,649 --> 00:14:30,332
Who knows the boss didn't want to sell it

150
00:14:30,532 --> 00:14:34,860
That's good
I don't have to help you with those strange problems

151
00:14:35,060 --> 00:14:37,885
This time,it's simple

152
00:14:38,085 --> 00:14:39,758
No way

153
00:14:39,958 --> 00:14:43,026
You say it all the time
But it's never easy

154
00:14:43,226 --> 00:14:44,384
I swear

155
00:14:44,584 --> 00:14:45,497
I promise

156
00:14:45,697 --> 00:14:48,545
I won't get you in any trouble this time

157
00:14:52,807 --> 00:14:55,955
Ye Zi,just help me

158
00:14:56,155 --> 00:14:57,743
I won't trouble you

159
00:14:57,943 --> 00:15:02,403
As long as you help me,
I will get that poster definitely

160
00:15:02,603 --> 00:15:04,079
How come

161
00:15:04,279 --> 00:15:06,922
She wasn't willing to sell it to me
not mention you

162
00:15:07,122 --> 00:15:09,731
Don't ask

163
00:15:09,931 --> 00:15:14,392
I'll get you the poster
as long as you help me

164
00:15:19,645 --> 00:15:21,316
Ye Zi

165
00:15:22,305 --> 00:15:23,800
OK,shoot

166
00:15:27,757 --> 00:15:29,363
Send the love letter to Yuan Lang

167
00:15:29,563 --> 00:15:30,249
What

168
00:15:36,716 --> 00:15:37,609
Painter

169
00:15:37,809 --> 00:15:41,151
How come do you come so late

170
00:15:41,351 --> 00:15:42,775
The lesson was over just now

171
00:15:42,975 --> 00:15:44,482
You always have reasons

172
00:15:48,806 --> 00:15:49,483
What is it

173
00:15:54,122 --> 00:15:54,850
Love letter?

174
00:15:57,181 --> 00:16:01,265
Is it for me?

175
00:16:05,456 --> 00:16:06,876
No

176
00:16:07,076 --> 00:16:08,194
Love letter?

177
00:16:08,394 --> 00:16:11,839
Boys send you a love letter
several days after enrollment?

178
00:16:12,039 --> 00:16:14,654
Can they focus on painting

179
00:16:14,854 --> 00:16:16,408
Is it Xiang Zeyi?

180
00:16:16,608 --> 00:16:17,486
What are you talking about

181
00:16:17,686 --> 00:16:20,802
I don't know him well

182
00:16:21,002 --> 00:16:21,548
Who sent it

183
00:16:23,132 --> 00:16:25,962
Boys in Art College only know how to send love letters

184
00:16:26,162 --> 00:16:26,932
Stop

185
00:16:27,132 --> 00:16:30,394
This is from Zhu Zi

186
00:16:32,613 --> 00:16:33,876
Zhu Xuan?

187
00:16:37,670 --> 00:16:42,846
I'm so worried and at a loss
I have to ask you for help

188
00:16:45,391 --> 00:16:51,805
OK,it's normal in today's society

189
00:16:52,005 --> 00:16:57,768
We can't take people's rights to chase love from them

190
00:16:57,968 --> 00:17:00,140
It's true

191
00:17:00,340 --> 00:17:04,090
But I don't feel well

192
00:17:04,290 --> 00:17:06,330
I wanted to refuse

193
00:17:06,530 --> 00:17:11,163
But I can't let her suffer
after all we are good friends for years

194
00:17:11,363 --> 00:17:13,244
What do you mean by "you wanted to refuse"

195
00:17:13,444 --> 00:17:15,694
You two are good friends

196
00:17:15,894 --> 00:17:18,590
-Only good friends
-True

197
00:17:18,790 --> 00:17:21,106
That's totally correct

198
00:17:21,306 --> 00:17:25,999
But is it fair for Zhu Xuan and Yuan Lang

199
00:17:26,199 --> 00:17:32,448
Just like you said,everyone has rights to love
We can't kill it when it just begins

200
00:17:32,648 --> 00:17:33,846
What were you saying

201
00:17:34,046 --> 00:17:35,687
What does that relate to my senior

202
00:17:35,887 --> 00:17:36,614
Of course

203
00:17:39,328 --> 00:17:41,535
Should I give it to Yuan Lang

204
00:17:45,610 --> 00:17:46,820
You scared me

205
00:17:47,020 --> 00:17:47,924
Pardon?

206
00:17:48,124 --> 00:17:48,748
Nothing

207
00:17:48,948 --> 00:17:50,160
Strange

208
00:17:50,360 --> 00:17:52,034
What to do

209
00:17:52,234 --> 00:17:53,432
Zhu Xuan wrote it?

210
00:17:53,632 --> 00:17:55,170
Give it to him

211
00:17:55,370 --> 00:17:59,440
Or it would be too late

212
00:18:02,461 --> 00:18:03,648
Please

213
00:18:03,848 --> 00:18:04,650
Why

214
00:18:04,850 --> 00:18:07,022
You two are so familiar
Of course you can do this

215
00:18:07,222 --> 00:18:08,966
You ask me to be your mail man?

216
00:18:09,166 --> 00:18:12,266
Don't mind

217
00:18:12,466 --> 00:18:17,422
Consider this as helping both of us

218
00:18:17,622 --> 00:18:20,078
Please

219
00:18:21,739 --> 00:18:24,100
Can't say no to you

220
00:18:24,300 --> 00:18:24,806
Thank you

221
00:18:25,006 --> 00:18:26,234
Bye

222
00:18:26,440 --> 00:18:27,280
Ask her to buy me a meal

223
00:18:47,420 --> 00:18:49,772
What's this
Love letter

224
00:18:49,772 --> 00:18:51,367
Love letter

225
00:18:55,159 --> 00:18:56,684
Yours?

226
00:18:59,170 --> 00:19:00,566
Yours

227
00:19:00,766 --> 00:19:02,938
Take it

228
00:19:03,138 --> 00:19:04,695
Mine?

229
00:19:04,895 --> 00:19:06,096
Open it

230
00:19:06,296 --> 00:19:07,809
Well

231
00:19:09,291 --> 00:19:11,311
It's inappropraite

232
00:19:11,511 --> 00:19:12,894
Why

233
00:19:13,094 --> 00:19:14,343
Just open it

234
00:19:14,540 --> 00:19:16,060
No

235
00:19:17,100 --> 00:19:18,840
I can't take it

236
00:19:21,000 --> 00:19:24,520
You can't take it then I will give it back to Zhu Xuan

237
00:19:24,719 --> 00:19:25,765
What

238
00:19:25,965 --> 00:19:27,062
It's from Zhu Xuan?

239
00:19:29,314 --> 00:19:31,500
You scared me
I thought

240
00:19:31,700 --> 00:19:32,531
You thought what

241
00:19:32,740 --> 00:19:33,820
I thought you don't want it

242
00:19:35,220 --> 00:19:37,040
Nothing

243
00:19:39,240 --> 00:19:40,600
I'll give it back

244
00:19:40,785 --> 00:19:41,739
No

245
00:19:42,845 --> 00:19:45,328
It's inappropriate to send it back

246
00:19:45,528 --> 00:19:49,648
Nothing inappropriate
I'll tell her that you've fallen in love with another woman

247
00:19:49,860 --> 00:19:50,540
Nonsense

248
00:19:57,560 --> 00:19:58,940
Open it

249
00:20:06,640 --> 00:20:09,155
Dear brother
Hello

250
00:20:09,155 --> 00:20:10,433
This is Zhu Xuan

251
00:20:10,633 --> 00:20:12,223
What are you doing

252
00:20:12,423 --> 00:20:13,334
Let me have a look

253
00:20:13,534 --> 00:20:14,411
It's for me not you

254
00:20:14,611 --> 00:20:15,382
You can't see

255
00:20:15,582 --> 00:20:17,235
The girl who told you a cold joke

256
00:20:17,435 --> 00:20:19,403
But

257
00:20:20,211 --> 00:20:23,355
If it's possible,
could you forget that joke

258
00:20:23,555 --> 00:20:24,933
Forget it

259
00:20:25,133 --> 00:20:27,707
Actually,I can tell more cold jokes

260
00:20:28,957 --> 00:20:30,723
You look in love

261
00:20:35,603 --> 00:20:36,345
No

262
00:20:47,284 --> 00:20:48,247
How's it

263
00:20:48,447 --> 00:20:49,257
Well

264
00:20:51,001 --> 00:20:52,124
What

265
00:20:54,892 --> 00:20:56,334
Mission completed

266
00:20:56,534 --> 00:20:58,109
Enjoy it by yourself

267
00:20:58,309 --> 00:20:59,359
Where are you going

268
00:21:09,330 --> 00:21:10,755
Ye Zi

269
00:21:10,955 --> 00:21:12,131
Eat more

270
00:21:14,808 --> 00:21:17,129
Well

271
00:21:17,329 --> 00:21:19,123
Did you send it for me

272
00:21:19,323 --> 00:21:21,867
Yes,just wait

273
00:21:24,732 --> 00:21:26,181
Look at you

274
00:21:26,381 --> 00:21:31,787
What if he feels nothing after reading it

275
00:21:31,987 --> 00:21:34,065
Impossible

276
00:21:35,588 --> 00:21:43,298
What I gave him on that letter was pure love

277
00:21:47,513 --> 00:21:49,627
He will definitely react to me

278
00:21:49,827 --> 00:21:52,530
We shall see

279
00:21:52,730 --> 00:21:59,813
He will finally be mine

280
00:22:01,779 --> 00:22:02,723
Scary

281
00:22:08,147 --> 00:22:10,657
I've sent it for you
Where's my poster

282
00:22:14,405 --> 00:22:15,196
Well

283
00:22:15,396 --> 00:22:16,165
Zhu Zi

284
00:22:16,365 --> 00:22:18,512
Are you trying to hide

285
00:22:18,712 --> 00:22:19,877
No

286
00:22:20,759 --> 00:22:22,943
I'm Zhu Xuan

287
00:22:23,143 --> 00:22:28,263
I will fufill my promise
and take you to find the poster tonight

288
00:22:28,463 --> 00:22:29,830
Promise?

289
00:22:30,030 --> 00:22:31,525
Yes

290
00:22:53,126 --> 00:22:54,508
What are we doing here

291
00:22:55,753 --> 00:22:56,546
Be queit

292
00:22:58,172 --> 00:23:00,336
I'm observing

293
00:23:00,536 --> 00:23:03,460
Why are you acting like a thief

294
00:23:06,827 --> 00:23:09,157
What are you doing

295
00:23:09,357 --> 00:23:10,607
Be quiet

296
00:23:13,676 --> 00:23:16,433
Take the poster

297
00:23:16,633 --> 00:23:18,112
Take the poster?

